    <div>
        <h1>Goku</h1>
        <p><strong>Universe:</strong> Universe 7</p>
        <p><strong>Role:</strong> Hero</p>
        <p><strong>Species:</strong> Saiyan</p>

        <h2>Backstory</h2>
        <p>
            Goku was an alien sent to Earth to conquer the planet but he accidentally hit his head and became the Goku we know today.
        </p>

        <h2>Abilities</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Kamehameha</li>
            <li>Instant Transmission</li>
            <li>Ultra Instinct</li>
            <li>Spirit Bomb</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>First Appearance</h2>
        <p>Dragon Ball Episode 1</p>
    </div>
</div>

